high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward then turn left to face the counter.
Open the cupboard that's under the counter to the right of the stove and grab the plate that's down there then close the door.
Take a small step to your left.
Look up and warm the plate in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the plate to the left of the sink.

Put the plate inside the microwave above the stove, heat it, remove it and close the door.

Put the heated plate on the counter to the left of the sink.
